
{{define "subject"}}Verify your Jobman account{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi,

Thanks for signing up for Jobman. To activate your account, use the verification token below.

Verification token: {{.activationToken}}

To activate, send a PUT request to /v1/users/activate with the token in the request body:

    curl -X PUT http://localhost:4000/v1/users/activate \
      -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
      -d '{"token": "{{.activationToken}}"}'

This token expires in 3 days. If you didn't create a Jobman account, you can safely ignore this email.

---
Jobman — job application tracker
This is an automated message. Please do not reply.
{{end}}

{{define "htmlBody"}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verify your Jobman account</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { padding: 40px 16px; }
    .card { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; }
    .header { background: #1a1a1a; padding: 24px 32px; }
    .header-title { margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .body { padding: 32px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 15px; color: #18181b; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .intro { font-size: 15px; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 28px; }
    .token-box { background: #f4f4f5; border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 0 0 28px; text-align: center; }
    .token-label { font-size: 11px; color: #a1a1aa; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .token-value { font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #18181b; margin: 0; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
    .note { background: #eff6ff; border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 0 0 28px; }
    .note p { font-size: 13px; color: #1e40af; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    .note code { font-size: 12px; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; }
    .disclaimer { font-size: 13px; color: #a1a1aa; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 28px; }
    .footer { border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e7; padding-top: 20px; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #a1a1aa; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <p class="header-title">Jobman</p>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <p class="greeting">Hi there,</p>
        <p class="intro">
          Thanks for signing up. To activate your account, use the verification token below.
          It expires in <strong>3 days</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="token-box">
          <p class="token-label">Your verification token</p>
          <p class="token-value">{{.activationToken}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="note">
          <p>
            Send a <code>PUT /v1/users/activate</code> request with this token in the request body to activate your account.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="disclaimer">
          If you didn't create a Jobman account, you can safely ignore this email.
          No account will be activated without this token.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>Jobman — job application tracker<br>This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
{{end}}
